description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Luteovulum sphaeroides; Rhodobacter sphaeroides; Rhodococcus capsulatus; Rhodococcus minor; Rhodopseudomonas sphaeroides; Rhodopseudomonas spheroides; Rhodorhagus capsulatus; Rhodorhagus minor; Rhodorrhagus capsulatus; Rhodorrhagus spheroides; Rhodosphaera capsulata; Rhodosphaera minor.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
